types.title: Architect
types.description: Imaginative and strategic thinkers, with a plan for everything.

types.title: Logician
types.description: Innovative inventors with an unquenchable thirst for knowledge.

types.title: Commander
types.description: Bold, imaginative and strong-willed leaders, always finding a way – or making one.

types.title: Debater
types.description: Smart and curious thinkers who cannot resist an intellectual challenge.

types.title: Advocate
types.description: Quiet and mystical, yet very inspiring and tireless idealists.

types.description: Poetic, kind and altruistic people, always eager to help a good cause.

types.title: Logistician
types.description: Practical and fact-minded individuals, whose reliability cannot be doubted.

types.title: Defender
types.description: Very dedicated and warm protectors, always ready to defend their loved ones.

types.description: Excellent administrators, unsurpassed at managing things – or people.

types.title: Consul
types.description: Extraordinarily caring, social and popular people, always eager to help.

types.title: Virtuoso
types.description: Bold and practical experimenters, masters of all kinds of tools.

types.title: Adventurer
types.description: Flexible and charming artists, always ready to explore and experience something new.

types.title: Entrepreneur

types.description: Spontaneous, energetic and enthusiastic people – life is never boring around them.
